{"tid":891978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本巴士駕駛反抗前輩換檔指示 班次延誤","createTime":"2018-11-06T14:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T14:45:11.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1f7522f4fa2df0d58c919bbb9ae1c3245ebfeebc","tid":891978,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"日本德島海部觀光由阿南發往大阪的高速巴士今年6月一名50多歲男性駕駛因為反抗同車隨車指導員的指示,而在行程途中將車開往淡路島南休息站停車,並讓17名乘客下車後罷駛,17名乘客等了1個多小時才有另一輛車來接駁.<br />\n <br />\n該巴士公司及德島運輸局表示,該名巴士駕駛才剛進公司,<br />\n但由於其行車時排檔檔位一直處於低速檔,所以隨車指導員指示他要換檔成高速檔,該名駕駛拒不服從,並開入休息站<br />\n後,拒絕再開車,而隨車指導員因為沒有做行車前的健康檢查所以無法代替其開車, 車上17名乘客則苦等一個多小時才坐上下一班開往大阪的班次."},{"pid":"fbf6f780b69fad94ddf5e52811c4829fabb8de25","tid":891978,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:15:12.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"3d6b4fe47bcce57dd6ce1d2024184d5a424fb328","tid":891978,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79587a5d24d1826ae376c2d59e55b79f13c7c66","tid":891978,"uid":36901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"觀光巴士好大壓力<br />\n成日爆"},{"pid":"4dc90c964c813e38b2a7c0265e7a0a97de0b3415","tid":891978,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:37:36.000Z","msg":"架佬真係變撚態又自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa20aa72475801cea2e83813b73fdf4eb9a5fa0","tid":891978,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T14:45:11.000Z","msg":"邪魔だ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}